\begin_inset Formula $g\in G$
\end_inset

 (unitarity of 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{g}$
\end_inset

 is trivial to prove for symmetry groups where 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

 is a rotation and/or translation).
\end_layout

