\end_inset

 are partner functions of different irreducible representations 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha\neq\beta$
\end_inset

, or if they correspond to different components 
\begin_inset Formula $i\neq j$
\end_inset

 of the same (unitary) representation 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=\beta$
