\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

) by some scalar 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon(\vec{x)}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu(\vec{x})=1$
\end_inset

 , and we want to find the resulting time-harmonic electric field 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{E}(\vec{x})e^{-i\omega t}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
