\begin_inset Formula $\hat{A}$
\end_inset

 is some linear operator and 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{b}$
\end_inset

 is some known right-hand side proportional to the current density 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{J}$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

